Study start-up timeline in PREVENT-HD. To respond to the public health crisis presented by COVID-19, study start-up timelines for PREVENT-HD were accelerated. From first draft of the protocol to first participant enrolled required only 127 days. 
   FDA, Food and Drug Administration; 
